Cdata.Note: - Backstory : Bastard Son of the Holy Empire. Vale is the family name of his mother taking it for his own protection as he is kept hidden from the public as he is Half Elf. Even with his clear hatred from the People of the Castle he maintains the worship to their god and remains loyal to the Church. While he is 15, a rogue servant would reveal the secret of the young prince to the Public which caused him to flee and would later be sent to Freedom Academy.

Abilities.Dark Flames:
Elements Dark and Fire
Action type: Special Ability 
Skill descriptions:  The user would merge both Fire and Dark magic together making flames colored similar to purple. The dark flames are much stronger making it a 2dmagic+dstr attack

Cdata.Note:
- Backstory: Formerly know as Vinny Nibbona, he was just your average Italian immigrant with a lot of connections to the mob in the height of the American prohibition era, unfortunately after amassing a fortune and aiming to retire he was gunned down outside his house by the police. 

Then he awoke, he was small, his body felt odd, there was a woman, she was pale as snow as she was holding something large, what was it? as his weary vision focused on the woman she was biting into a man's neck, he screamed and she stopped, dropping the corpse to the ground, and thus began his new life, his new wonderful powerful life, he will enjoy this life and become unopposed by all so that he may achieve true freedom. 

For now though, he needs time to build his power so he'll play nice till graduation, or atleast act nice and hide the not so nice parts.

Backstory: Azures home world is ran by high end family of shoguns that she was born into as a soon to be heir-- destined leader of shogunate. The thoughts of running the palace was one day stricken from her by a revenge plot thought up my small army of Ronins attempting to assassinate her family, the only way she was able to flee with her life was by the use of her mothers own magic, sending her off to a different world to be safe. Natural gifted with a blade, she meditates on the thought of one day returning to obtain revenge on the people that tried to end her bloodline.

Abilities.Zanmato:
Character: Off
Elements Light
Action type: Active
Skill descriptions: The user glides the palm of their hand from the base of their weapon's blade to the tip, enchanting it with a divinity. The users blade deals 50% extra damage to everyone hit by it while enchanted or 100% damage to anyone who can use dark magic or is weak to light magic. 


Skill drawback: The enchanting effect can last only one swing, meaning its a one use spell. Even if it lands a strike one turn after activation, the entire effect will be gone. It lasts until an attack is successful though. 2 turn cooldown

Abilities.Raging Grasp:
Character: Off
Elements Fire
Action type: Active
Skill descriptions: The user manifests their magic into a heated grasp or touch. It can be changed like a dial from a warm touch into a scorching heat that burns through defenseless targets like butter. If touching a conductive source then it can cause combustion or a fiery glow through flickering flames.

Effect: 75% bonus damage when using fire magic

Skill drawback: the user takes 25% recoil when using it

Cdata.Note: Personality: He's a jokester enjoying messing with people here and there but nothing to bad he often will get himself in trouble due to this tho.

- Backstory:  Zarall was born into a royal family well know for fire magic but one day Zarall got introduced to     
traveling to different worlds at 13. He decided to go across worlds to learn new techniques and knowledge and eventually learned how to use lighting magic. One day while studying  a guy came up to him  and handed him a letter with a invation to join a college. After discussing with his family they paid for him to go to the college.

Abilities.Soul Corridor - Unnamed Goblina: The user can summon the attached unnamed Goblina to their location regardless of the Goblinas location. If Goblina dies, she is forcibly summoned

Cdata.Note: - Backstory: Raise in the Kingdom of Dragon to be a great warrior. He would dream to rule his own land as a Lord of his own inspired by the Ruler of Kingdom of Dragon as he appeared to be a godlike being.

Born and raised by a Lycanthrope Trainer and then was lost during some circumstances and lost far away from them. Started training alone gathering food for survival. In search of more power the individual started roaming around the world practicing his skills and improving fighting people. Lacked what were called 'friends' .

Personality: He’s pretty introverted, not liking large crowds. Tends to keep to himself and focuses on getting stronger rather than meddling in people’s business. Though he will do it if he thinks he can handle it.

Born in the Kingdom of Dwargon to a Consort of a noble. She was raised in servitude. She snuck out in the middle of the night to read from her masters library quite often and ended up enthralled with books. She often times got scolded for it by her mother but rarely did anything come of it. She ended up reading through the entire library and right as she finished. She got a letter saying she was invited to the school on a scholarship to attend. Her mother rushed her out of the house and she ended going to ingrassia.

Behind the scenes however, every time she snuck into the library, her mother was beaten by their lord, time and time again trying to protect her daughter, she lied about who entered his study. And when Alyasha left, the lord got pissed that a servant left on her own without consulting him. Avoiding that interaction was her mothers intent but its unlikely that her mother will live much longer under the circumstances. Lets hope news doesnt reach alyasha

Abilities.Divine Instruments pt1:
Light: Crown of Versprechredi: Can be used to produce a magical piece of paper, if signed and documented, then stamped with the blood of all parties, it bursts into flames. If any party violates the contract, they suffer the consequences listed in the contract

Dark: Cloak of Schicksantracht: The user can drain restore her health by defending against a magic attack, if the users magic stat is higher than the roll of the attack, its ignored and heals her instead. She cannot attack while she is equipped with the cloak

Earth: Chalice of Gelduh: The user can pour her magic into it and allow a 1 time use item for anyone to use her magic stat instead of their own. Takes a turn to pour magic into it.

Wind: Shield of Schutzaria: Puts up a sphere shaped shield equal to 1xmagic, if that runs out, she can choose to sacrifice health instead of letting the shield fall. Anyone who holds malice or intends to cause harm towards the user or anyone within the sphere cannot enter. If they are within the border, they are roughly ejected. Attempting to attack the sphere is thrown back after damage is dealt unless the shield breaks. 

Fire: Spear of Leidenschaft:  1 turn charge up, 1dmagic, cannot be defended and breaks through any barriers. returns to the user if thrown.

Water: Staff of Flutrane: The user can use the staff to heal EVERYONE in the channel. Friend and foe alike, she cannot choose which to heal. 1dmagic heal, afterwards she cant move for 2 turns.
Abilities.Divine Instruments pt2:
Life: (Requires all 6 elements to create the Life element) Sword of Ewigeliebe: 2 effects 
1. Can be used to temporarily summon winter, causing everything around to become iced and cold. Takes a turn

2. (Can only be used during winter) The user swings the sword to give all opponents disadvantage for 2 turns and summons feybeasts (random creatures of my choosing) to attack for them. Mag/5 feybeasts can be summoned. Each attacks and defends with 1dmagic and has a health of 1xmagic/2. If attacked with fire, they cannot defend. The user cannot attack while feybeasts are active and Passes out for 2 hours upon the last feybeasts death. Cannot be dispelled until combat is over

Skill drawback: The user can only summon instruments for elements she has. Each instrument requires 3 turns to summon and taking damage higher that 10% of her hp during its charge up nullifies the time spent charging up and she has to start over. Her magic stat is decreased by 50% for every instrument summoned after the first.

Cdata.Note:
Backstory:he  was born into a family of angels, the parents soon found out that he somehow had daemon blood and was part daemon, so after finding out about his genetics he tossed aside like trash and forgotten about, he was a starving kid until a great daemon found him and kept him safe, not wanting to corrupt his already corrupt blood he refused to show him how to use his magic, though he watched and studied how he did. They stayed together traveling from place to place till they settled down in a village somewhere he can’t remember. But one day in the middle of the night, their house was broken into and his companion was killed. 

He was abducted and experimented on by the humans , 
He was forced to kill people, animals, beast, he was tortured and experimented on by them leaving multiple scars on his body, including a very large one on his face. The very Day they decided to finally kill him off he broke and had enough of what they had been doing to him, we learned how to do the magic that his daemon companion did, it was a art that only a few knew…blood magic, he escaped and killed all his captors and has been traveling since.

Abilities.Blood-Red Commander Igris’s armor:
Character: (Proxy off)
Elements (dark)
Action type: active/ passive 
Skill descriptions: 2dmag
The user makes himself armor of his blood whatever he rolls gets a separate health bar for his armor

Skill drawback:  The user has to use 25% of his current health to conjure up armor made from his blood this takes two attacking turns yet he can still block to protect himself from getting knocked out, he will not block with his armor he will just tank attacks, unless it breaks he can block to prevent himself from taking more damage
Abilities.bloodlust:
Character: (Proxy off)
Elements (dark)
Action type: active/passive 
Skill descriptions: if he consumes blood from someone he goes into a bloodlust and does double damage with any attack, the passive can surpass the time limit if he drinks blood again before it ends yet if he does the cooldown doubles, if he damages his opponent with a sharp weapon he can drink their blood.

Skill drawback:the double damage only works if the attack hits and only doubles the amount hit, the passive takes 25% of his current health, this passive lasts for 5 turns. If the passive ends I get a 5 turn attack stun
Abilities.lifesteal:
Character: (Proxy-off)

Skill descriptions: after he attacks he gets the damage/2 for his life steal by drinking their blood

Skill drawback:  two turn attack stun and disadvantage on next attack turn

Cdata.Note: She was born to a family of Lycanthropes that directly serves the beast king. All of them are black snakes however she was born as pure as snow. It started a discussion of adultery and thus she was never loved. The fact that she was born with a skill that prevented her from making any noise, whether it be from steps, breathing, heartbeat, or her own voice. She can never make a sound. Causing her parents to be paranoid whenever they begin to speak unaware of their cursed daughters location. Eventually she was picked by the beast king himself to be trained as an assassin. He quickly delegated the work, he was a proud warrior, not an assassin and therefore had nothing to teach her. The person that was going to teach her though, feared her talents and kidnapped her and shipped her off to the academy. She isnt mad, frankly she is unsure if she can even feel mad. She had suppressed everything for her entire life. Why would she start feeling stuff now?

Cdata.Note: Backstory: her kind after birth stays in caccon developing for 12 years. They come out of the cooccon with the mental age of 10 year old then depend next 8 years learning in the community. Only after then they would leave the community to find themselves and try to make communities else where. She no different finding the best way to make community through power so through hardships she managed to enter the academy to become stronger.

Backstory: He was literally born inside of a field of battle and that is all it took to twist his mind to see war and combat as the most entertaining thing in the world. Combat of all kinds isn't nice to him though, he needs to feel the beat of his heart because it isn't a real fight to him if he isn't, this obsession lead to him joining bandits because of the pursuit of never-ending bloodshed. This seemed like the life for him, but he quickly turned on the group after they attempted to assault someone who already gave in and couldn't fight back, which is an objection to his moral compass. Despite his thirst for fighting, he isn't blinded by it because he knows when one should end or when it is just beginning. Seeking to see more to the world than combat (If there is such a thing as more), he joins an academy to find something to mask his hunger, which turns out to be the places food. For the time being.

Abilities.Raging Bull:
Character: On
Elements None
Action type: Active
Skill descriptions:  User brings out the deepest bellows of their rage and puts it all into their strength causing it to double for 3 turns. Notably, the user's muscle mass will increase greatly in all parts of their body while they may show animalistic traits. These traits include, but are not limited to: Growling, salivating, intensive staring, yelling, and a change in fighting style (Moving on all fours, biting, clawing, or spasming hits, ect.).

Skill drawback: For a 6 additional turns after use, the user's strength is halved. This causes the user to show great signs of exhaustion, panting, slowed movements, and muscle fatigue. During the 6 turns, the user's endurance will also be halved due to expending their muscles to lengths they they are not supposed to be.
